    "image": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6a/Ruins_of_St_Mary%27s_Abbey%2C_Melrose_%28Scotland%27s_first_Cistercian_monastery%2C_1136%29%2C_showing_late_14th-century_Gothic_architecture_in_rose-colored_sandstone_with_medieval_cemetery%2C_burial_place_of_Robert_the_Bruce%27s_heart%2C_Scottish_Borders.jpg/330px-thumbnail.jpg",
